values:
I just feel so… off. Not right. I want to go home so badly. I don’t know why I ever agreed to come here. My suggestions of places closer to home and car trips were obviously not enough… but now this is too much. I can’t do it. I’m not good at new situations and new places. I like the comfort of the habitual… and I don’t care how lame that makes me. I like things a lot better when I know what’s coming next. I want my bed, and my Milo, and my Simpsons and my bowl, and then I just want to pass the fuck out and wake up around 11 tomorrow.

But no. I’m here. Sleeping alone. Where I will wake up ten times during the night and have no one here to comfort me. No way to go home. Nothing familiar to do. I don’t care that this makes me a big baby. I don’t like new places and new things and I’m incredibly content with my home.  I have a million and one things to do, and the panic I’m feeling makes me feel as if nothing will get done this week…. And its not like I wasn’t already freaking out about my grades this year already. FUCK MY LIFE. Why did I agree to this?

I want my mommy.

Way to make me feel absolutely disgusting and then ignoring me you gigantic asshole.

Posted via LiveJournal.app.

I'm pretty sure I've lost any aeota of respect i may have had left for matt. 
he's disgusting and slimy and maipulative. he's completely insecure and selfish. and i honestly don't think he knows how to be a good boyfriend. 
i don't think i can hang out with him anyomre... i don't know how she lets him do this o her. you should NOT be fighting after 5 months about the same things you were fighting about after 2. it's just NOT meant to be. he's a head case. and he's going to hurt her. and then I'll have to kill him.

How the eff do I always get sucked into this shit. I'm so tucking sick of matt. He bores me to tears. Travelling at 2km an hour across the city to look at effing welding helmets. Ew. Next time go by yourselves. And now talking about how yard sale.money can help buy his helmet. WTF. Cause you have a few things at home to sell? May I remind you that you basically live there rent free? Meg he's walking all over you. You give him too much and he's pretty useless. If she wasn't looking for a job for him would he be? Ugh I think he's so... Below her.

Posted via LiveJournal.app.

i really am dumb sometimes. maybe dumb's not the word... unnecessarily curious? that tend to foster less than appealing consequences?
... putting it lightly. 

i just don't know why i get myself involved with boys i don't think i can actually see myself with. i'll just end up hurting him... i wanted to give it a try though... a beta male if you will.. because apparently i clash too much with the alphas... but ive come to the conclusion that the betas are just BORING! where's the excitement? the adventure? the cocky attitude? the "i can whisk you away and you're going to like it" demeanor? I want the unpredictable actions and ambitions that i come to expect from myself. 
and i need a bit of fire... and oddly enough its HIS end it isnt coming from. not since marco have i felt so undesireable lol. he won't even touch me. i'd say its affecting my ego, but i just feel like he's intimidated. And that, on top of everythign else is a huge turn off. I realize that yes, I am a little more experienced than most.. but when its that obvious its almost a teachign session to the point where it isnt enjoyable anymore. Maybe i should give him the benefit of the doubt... but then that leaves room for disappointment... and is this even what i want? why would i add another name to a list that im not even sure i want there?

honestly, being single was so much simpler.

I just feel that maybe HE'S the one not putting in the greatest bit of effort? Like Meg is not some island you have now claimed posession over. And I try SO hard to like him but then he does stupid shit like tonight and she gets all upset and quiet, and that makes me angry that he can hurt her so bad with somethign so trivial.These things shouldnt matter to him!! 
And like, I HATE having to tip toe around matt. he's not even my boyfriend and i feel like i have to watch everythign i say around him so he doesn't get offended. Like, guys names can't be mentionned because apparently guys and girls can't just be friends.... Circle K can't be mentionned because its drama... its like i can't even tell meg about my day anymore because the SLIGHTEST thing will piss him off, and then she'll get all upset when she sure as fuck doesnt need that. 
I just want to slap im sometimes.... personally, this level of insecurity and control at this stage in the relationship would be setting off warning bells.

It's crazy how much someone can change
In such a short amount of time.
Someone you thought you knew inside out,
Take a bullet for you without a doubt.
The good times a not so distant memory,
I just don't get why he takes priority over me.

Friends for life, chicks before dicks
And all that shit.
Last time I checked, friends don't ditch.

Posted via LiveJournal.app.

it's really hard to be happy for someone else when you're so miserable in your own life. 
i did the worst i could possibly do last semester and even got an email that warned me about academic probation. i have no job and thus no money. and to make me feel a little worse about myself, lets just throw in the fact that I've become the 5th wheel in my own house. 
and i know that i presented the image that this is what i want to do... but i really miss him. like heart ache miss him. and i wonder if its love or loneliness, but the longer its been the worse i feel. hes not a bad person, and he does have the best intentions no matter what everyone says about him. but its so hard to defend something for so long and only get negative responses. the only time i ever got agreement is when i had a complaint. i know he's not perfect, but who is? maybe hes what i need to keep the fire and balance me out. maybe... not...? i dont know. im so confused. 
i just want to feel better.

So Eric just came and rescued me. He's such a good guy. He made me go for a walk around the General to calm down and bought me a coffee... HOw is it that some adults fully respect us twenty-somethings and others still see us as small children? If my intellect is greater than yours, where do you get the audacity to talk down to me?
UGH 
anyways he told me that since im casual i never have to work on this floor again if i dont want and i can still keep my job here and he's trying to hook me up in health records... so he really set my mind at ease. we'll see what happens... I"ll keep you posted of course.

i am literally seconds away from quitting this fucking job.
i want to beat heather perkins' face in with a heavy, blunt object. I'm sure it would actually improve her appearance. 
seriously though, if bich paid more attention to what she ate instead of shit that was none of her business, I'm sure we'd BOTH be more cheerful individuals. Like, I am not even on her unit today. She came down to the effing floor, stuck her nose over my shoulder and said, hmmm, i guess youre being paid today to surf the net? FUCK YOU BITCH. You have NO CLUE whats going on down here, or how much i accomplished this morning, or the fact that theres NOTHIGN FOR ME TO DO RIGHT NOW. AAAAND to piss me off even more, she went upstairs and told the case managers that i'm being a slacker down here. Nicole's all like, be careful, they're all talking about you eh?
But why? Honestly? Do you all have nothign better to do? And this has been going on for at least the last two years... I really just dont feel that i should be persecuted like this. If you have an issue with me, tell me to my face, dont tell everyone else except me. 
This place has made me cry for the last time...

Or at least it would be if I didn't have to work.
Oh how I love boxing day. The mad mall rush, the huge sales! It's so exhilirating.... and of course I'm missing it. But there's always the weekend :) I can't wait... not that i really NEED anythign... but you know how i am about pretty new things... nothing makes me happier :)
Oops. I totally forgot to get anything for my dad & step mom.... maybe i should bake some more of my snowball cookies? So good and SO easy. Literally 5 min to prepare lol. That's a good plan if i do say so myself. 

Anyhoo, on a totally unrelated topic, APPARENTLY men have no imagination AT ALL. lol. THREE different nurses have told me their boyfriends popped the question xmas eve/morning. Original, no? Whatever happened to romance? I remember when Virginia told me she was engaged... now THAT was a cute one.... he said he had to go on a business trip and invited her along and then while he was at his "meeting" he made the preparations and later popped the question reminding her that it was that time of year 5 years ago that they first met <3 <3 <3 Now THAT is romance. Oh Boys.

Merry Christmas, Happy New Year, and all that Jazz. 
It's funny how I only really write when I work... which is becoming more and more sparatic.  Shame on me. But yes, I'm at work on Christmas day. Good times. I'd complain.. but I get time and a half... so realllyyyyyy I can't lol. Considering how poor i am, this is much needed. 
I don't really like being home so much though. Way too much to do around the house at all times. And milo hates it. He misses his Beau Kitty so much. And I'm so freaking lonely. At least I'll have company for new year's. But not going downtown this year... laaame. no reason to get all fancy :( Oh well, I'll make up my own reasons and get all pretty anyways. 

So I've been talking to Rahman a lot over the break... he really is a sweetheart. It think things just started on the wrong foot... I kinda think I'd like to try things out a little in January... who knows? THere could be somethign there? There's just somethign about a strong guy with ambitions... so rare to find. And he's pretttyyyyyy. lol. But again.. the long run is SO uncertain. I mean... I have a whole new plan now. lol
Well... not so much NEW as I'm finally doing something aboutmy pipe dream.
I've decided to apply to FIT (fashion institute of tech) in New York City for fashion production! SOOO EXCITING! haha. Apply to a fashion house as an intern *sigh* that would be the life... But it will never happen unless I try... so tahts def the new plan of action. 

Alright, I'm assuming I should get somethign done today... peace
Cyanide & Happiness @ Explosm.net
Cyanide & Happiness @ Explosm.net

What is with my obsession with pretty brown boys? Honestly... too many to count. 
Last night was.. interesting. Never drinking that much again. But my costume was TOTALLY badass. Heck yes I was Cyndi Lauper. And NO i didn't copy Julia, I did it up about 50 million times better. So hah! lol. I even won a prize. Go team me. I definitely flirted with Rahman. I'm so bad. But I'm single so whatevs, right? We'll see what happens. 
Anyways, I should totally nurse this hangover.

Ahhh reading week. What was once eagerly looked forward to as a nice break and a trip home is now loathed. Littered with work and loneliness.... Ottawa is no fun anymore. 

Speaking of work, Gail and Christina Emery should die horrible horrible deaths. Basically, I've been shunned from recieving any shifts up in MDU. When asked why I was told I was the model employee; efficient, trained, liked by all the case managers; they just didn't want me up there anymore. Excuse you? I'm sorry, the only reasoning I can figure from that is christina, with her infinitly large head, doesn't like me. blame it on jealousy, or her newfound lesbian affair with Julie... either way, its cost me my full time cushy summer job. Fuck the politics in this place man. I have to run my own business. I can't stand the way people get promoted due to age and not ability. I wouldn't stand for it. And i MOST CERTAINLY would never stand for the blatant misuse of managerial power gail demonstrated. Not only was it incredibly low, but the mere fact that she told everyone else BUT me I was being denied shifts?? Completely unacceptable. I would have fired her on the spot. She's just lucky she doesn't HAVE a superior right now, otherwise I'd be writing a lengthy letter.
Cyanide & Happiness @ Explosm.net

sometimes i feel like such shit. 
i dont even know what happened... meg wasina super bad mood yesterday, and then she was sick all night long... so i didnt sleep.. but thats no reason for anxiety. Are they sympathy pains? Because i don't really want them. Its hard enough having to deal with it when something fucks up for me... let alone for someone else. 
And I'm so tired. i havent slept in 2 nights. Ican barely keep my eyes open. Maybe i'll nap in a tanning bed. 
i just dont get it though. I mean, I'm golden right now... school isnt stressful yet, friends are good, money sitch is good.... so whats my issue? lol. i want my mommy.

I'm so worried I'm losing arya as a friend. 
I mean, he's someone I've talked to EVERY DAY for almost a year and then ever since school started he's disappeared.... 
I mean, i know i complicate things.... but i want to be his friend so badly. He really is the most wonderful person. And he helped me through SO much.... I'd be devastated if he said he never wanted to talk to me again :(
Cyanide & Happiness @ Explosm.net

I had this incredibly horrible dream last night... 
Marco was with Diane and i practically chased him down and confessed my undying love for him, and then he blew me off. I bawled the WHOLE dream I'm pretty sure. It was sad in a pathetic kinda way. 
Its SO werid though. Because while i DONT like Diane, I definitely don't want marco in that way anymore.... I mean, yes he's still a wonderful person... lol just too Marco now. 
I think I'm just jealous of what he has right now. I just want to date again. I know I'm capable of it... I don't know why I don't just do it.

I'm not even with him, so I'm not entirely sure how I'm getting my heart broken. Sunny, or Sundeep rather, apparently has a girlfriend. Which makes perfect sense. I mean, why else would he not want to take me anywhere public or acknowledge that we were practically dating? But like.... why would he want to see me so often? Or say those things he said? If he DOES have a girlfriend he definitely cheated on her. Does that mean that I'm the other girl? The dirty homewrecking bitch that he's sneaking around with? I feel so unclean. 
Are all men the same? 
At the same time though, it WAS joe who told me. And while they DO work together... Joe isn't exactly known for his honesty. That, and his immediate solution for revenge was sex with him of course. I obviously turned him down, but that seems a little too convenient, right? Ugh. I don't know who to trust or what to believe. Can any of them be trusted? Or are they constantly on the lookout for somethign better? somethign different? The moment the opportunity to dip their dick in a new pond comes a long they totally forget their commintments. I dont want to be someone's fogotten commitment.

So here i am exploring this crazy internet dating world... and I can't help but wonder how many of these boys have a word document saved with their "hello" speech and how man of them are genuinely interested in what i have to say. Yes, my mailbox is full, but it sure isn't interesting. 
Most of these boys just make me laugh. I'm a 22 year old girl. What gives you the idea that i want messages from some 40 yr old about his dick? do many 20 somethigns get off on that? If so, I'd like to meet them and just ask them what exactly is sexy about grey hairs and wrinkles? Or better yet, when i say i want direction I get 25 year old "gangstars" who live at home with mommy with no future aspirations at all...When mine talks about... finance? LOL the last thing i want to be is a sugar mamma. 
Whas even funnier are the boys that tell me "we have a lot in common." when i go to read their profiles i wonder if they've even read mine. maybe i should have a banner that flies proudy stating "geeks only!" There's nothing I hate more than someone with 5 different pictures of themselves flexing in the mirror. *gaaaaaaaaag*

So far, its a bust. But I'll let you know how this goes.

ITS MY LAST DAY AT CHEO!!!!!!

I'm so excited!!! And aww, everyone was SO sweet. They gave me flowers, and had a cake! I take back all the mean and cranky things i said about them.... Until next summer when I'm sure I'll get frustrated once more!

Now there's just shopping and packing left to do and then im FREE!!!! FREEEEEEEE AGAIN!!!! *sigh* I can't wait.

I may or may not have to break a former virgin's heart. i am a soulless asshole. 
I'm only human! We all have weaknesses! He was supposed to be a one night stand! He wasn't supposed to get attached... and now I'll be the bad guy. men do it ALL THE TIME. How do they feel no remorse? Stupid girly feelings. I mean, he's a nice guy, really... just not my type at all. This is so hard. I hate when people hate me.
Cyanide & Happiness @ Explosm.net

ITS MY LAST WEEK OF WORK! Celebrate good times, COME ON! lol

I guess i can officially celebrate Friday night as i prepare to leave Saturday morning on my wonderful Syracuse shopping excursion! I am SO excited lol. I dont think its healthy for one person to like shopping this much. And my list is huuuuge... maybe i should set myself a budget so i don't over do it? me... over do it? hahaha nevuuurrrr.

I'm also going to pay a visit to my dad tonight. I've been home all summer, I figure its about time. lol. Maybe I'll finally get my dress form! *sigh* wishful thinking, i know. but it never hurts lol. 

And in 2 weeks everyone will be moved in at school, and my life will get back to the wonderful normalcy that is school instead of this horrible thing people tell me is real life.

The sad part is that its true... except instead of other job postings, i gaze lovingly at the Trent U website, praying profusely for time to speed up and move in day to arrive. This place makes me feel like a brain dead drone, doing the same tasks over and over and over. I think I'm actually starting to get stupider. Meg's mom totally gave her an easy out out of her hell... we'll see how that unfolds. I on the other hand have to suck it up. As much as I want to set fire to this place and guage my eyes out everytime i have to make another photocopy... I feel like I'll want these guys on my side eventually..... Stupid well paying, bureaucratic, establishment. *shakes fist* Damn the Man. BUT there's only SIX MORE WORK DAYS!!! YAY!!!

My birthday is less than 2 weeks away. Normally at this time I would be hard at work picking out a killer outfit and planning a club night.... this year, i'm afraid, will not be the same. I'm incredibly sad.
Last year Shawn, Nic & Steve took me out and julia, sarah, tina, brian, SO many people stopped by, said hi, bought me a drink..... This year I have NO ONE in Ottawa to celebrate with, and LUCKY ME! My birthday falls on a Wednesday. yey. Ugh. I hate having no friends. 
THEN the weekend after is the long weekend, so everyone already has plans... and after that its already September! A birthday party in ptbo would turn into a welcome back party so fast that my event would be completely left out of the equation. :( Not that I had the greatest ptbo party last yr... but I'd at least like to TRY again. Ugh. Sadness. 

I know i should TRY to be jolly and make the best of it... but really when the last few have been so glamorous, it leaves a lot to live up to...

Ugh. I am so incredibly ticked off at the hospital right now. They have managed to block EVERY SINGLE web messenger service, and I have 2 weeks left of work. What the heck am I supposed to do with my time? Once again I was done all of my work by 10. This position is so pointless and definitely does NOT need a full time clerk to do it. What a waste of hospital money. But then again, they're quite good at doing that.

Speaking of finances, I was grossly disturbed to find out that Trent is no longer offering bursaries to students who do not receive OSAP. This leaves me incredibly confused. Forgive me if I'm wrong, but should bursaries not be awarded based on grades and NOT on the source your tuition comes from? Just because the governement isn't loaning me money, doesn't mean that I have to pay any less than anyone else. Not only is the money still coming out of my own pocket, but I had to work my ass off over the summer AND get a part time job during the school year to compensate for the fact that I couldn't save anythign, yet OSAP provides money based on cost of living expenses. What makes the situation even MORE frustrating is that it is a known fact that OSAP gives the student plenty, and the majority of them drink it away. They reffer to it as their "beer money cheques." So what makes a student who is technically doing everything they're supposed to do to make it through university on a budget, any less eligible?
Trent is Fucked Up man... 

Oh thank the good lord i got through their firewalls..... goddamn hospital.

i will not let this bother me.
i will not let this bother me. 
I WILL NOT LET THIS BOTHER ME.

Its funny how differently two people can interpret one person's actions. 
I don't feel so bad about petty nurses anymore. No matter who you are, or what your position is here, everyone is STILL going to talk about you. For example my poor poor Deanna. i LOVE this woman. She's strong and in control, and too funny and nice to eeeveryoooone. Well she's in charge, and since it's shut down she was like, don't call in the other nurses who are on vacay, I'll production line the blood drawing room.... so while she's doing somethign super fabulous for the burses that ARENT here, all the nurses who ARE, are just bitching about her behind her back. It's not cool man.
Not cool at all....

Men are assholes. I don't even fucking care how ridiculously repetitive I'm getting... it's true. 
Like... even the ones you think are sweethearts who have been in long term relationships are fucking jerks. They lead with their penises and have no sense of right and wrong. YES, even a kiss is cheating. So don't even try it. UGH MEN.

I am so incredibly mad at this whole fucking stupid unit. How the fuck do they expect me to survive the rest of the summer without using the internet? I mean... it is ELEVEN THIRTY and NO ONE has a job for me to do. except photocory. Which, personally, i consider an insult to my intelligence. "Can you make me 100 copies?" "Yes, and would you like me to sit there and watch the machine sort paper?" Like WTF. Thats not a job. 
And Rene is sooooooo fucking stupid. Like, I dont even know what his job is, but I can assure you, he isn't good at it. Like, his memory is shot worse than mine and I'm a pothead. And he's just... STUPID. I'm trying to tell him that cadence, the program we use to book apts, keeps fucking up and telling me it's 2029. Instead of calling IS and dealing with it, he's like, well maybe its cause you were on MSN, and when i told him no, i didnt install anything it was a WEB MESSENGER, he kept going on about installing software. Like WTF. Learn something about computers or AT LEAST the terminology. WEB means ONLINE. NO SOFTWARE. TOOL.

Guys are fucking stupid. Just fucking fucking fucking stupid. You tell me that I'm out of your league and its going to take a lot to impress me... and then you talk down to me like I'm twelve. Sorry, but I hardly think that that will make me like you... what do you think?
UGH. NO GOOD ONES LEFT!!
And seriously, fuck Sunny. Like, he couldn't be more what I'm looking for... but do you know what he SAID to me? That this "friendship" or whatever you want to call it is nothign... that if he saw me out in public, he may acknowledge my existence but that would be IT. UHM EXCUSE ME?! You'd better be damn proud to be my man... otherwise you can fuck right off.

god im in a bad mood.

So I'm reading all these old entries from like 04-05.... 

I would just like to clarify that I am well aware of how fucking STUPID i was when i was with Don. THANK GOD I wised up when I got older because i would NEVER put up with such a dead beat now.

I don't mean to sound stuck up... .but I'm waaaaaaay too good for this job. 
Yes, the money is wonderful, but it better damn well be for the bull shit that I have to put up with. It's like NOTHIGN gets done without me here! How did they ever survive the winter??

I just want out of here. To go home so badly. To go anywhere. I'm not cut out for this stupid monday to friday, get up at 6 every morning bull shit. It's just not me. Especially when I KNOW I could accomplish everything the girls do here in half the time. Why can't I come in at 10 and work til 4? I GAUREN-FUCKIN-TEE taht i will do MORe than them, and have it done better and more thoroughly. This is crap my friend.

I've been watching a lot of sex and the city lately... I think its incredibly depressing that I have the same cynical outlook on life as a group of forty somethign single women. I mean, I always knew I was mature and smart for my age... but 20 years wiser than i should be? lol. I feel like I shouldn't be so jaded yet. That I should work on being more like Charlotte and focus on being more positive. Maybe all the positive energy will bring me some positive vibes in return... who knows?
Also, whenever I feel like i hate children a lot and I dont fit the mold of a young woman taking the traditional steps of marriage and blah blah blah... I should watch the episode "A Woman's Right to Shoes." Because I DONT need to be traditional to be happy.

So i guess romance found me.... just not in the best way posiible. 

why am i setting myself up for hardcore heartbreak? we barely know each other and i already know it will hurt SO bad.
He's great. He's so pretty and easy to talk to... and kisses SO good. I swear though, if we had anythign else in common we'd be the same person...  he's just too perfect for me... but doesn't want a relationship. I dont know WHO left him fucked, but she did a damn good job of it. But like, i dont want to have to CONVINCE him to date me. I don't know why he doesn't just WANT to. 
And yes, I know, I don't even live here... if we WERE to date, there's that distance thing, as Meg's always SO quick to remind me. But quite frankly, I don't care. The distance doesn't bother me at all.
It's just him thats the obstacle... 
ugh. even when you think there's a good one left, there isnt.

Why oh Why is EVERY resident either married or already engaged???? They're only in their late twenties! Did they all scramble to find partners in med school for fear that the world would run out of girls? ugh its so frustrating. 
There are honestly NO good men left in this world.

Confidence, intelligence, and attractiveness are three characteristics that are near impossible to find in the same person. I'm so jaded. 

My horoscopes all seem to say that romance will find me mid-july.... we'll see what happens this week i guess... but i wont hold my breath.

Its so wrong. I'm disgusting. He's 3 years younger than me and he's sick. lol omg I'm dumb. but he's SO pretty. as if he brought his girlfriend to hang around here. and she's following him around like a love sick puppy... ew. but i get it though. he's adorable. 

Ugh. i just want to be a cute couple with someone. I'm so sick of this being single crap. I want someone to want me, and to get excited at the idea of spending time with me. Someone who isnt a total pervert and only after sex. Why is that so hard to find? I feel like the harder I look the less there is to be found.

EW. I fucking HATE julia. EW EW EW. i CANNOT express in words my incredible distaste for her. so she found my elvis tin. like a YEAR later. 20$ says she had it the whole time. Ew i hate her. And what i hate most is how the boys all choose her over me. CONSTANTLY. like, i can't even remember the last time i hung out with them all together, but they like, go downtown with her at least once a week. 

I am SO bored right now. I ran out of jobs a loooong time ago and now I'm just sitting on my ass. UGH. 
Whatevs. Lunch.

Meg started actual day camp today which means that I will now officially have no one to talk to while I'm at work all day. Sweet. I will be even more bored than i usually am. *grumble grumble* So unhappy about this. BUT we're hanging out again this weekend... and practically every weekend until the end of the summer... so I shouldn't complain too badly. 
I'm debating taking Friday off as well..... but I already had to take Monday off due to doctors appointments... so I guess thats good enough.

I had quite a boring Canada day this year though. It's so unfair that it fell on a Tuesday and everyone had to work the monday before.... Last year was so much fun, and Marco came down and all that good stuff.. this year was super lame. 
And like, my mom's like, WE can go downtown! but could she be any lamer? Like tahts EXACTLY what i want to do! Run into people downtown like Julia and reinforce the fact that I have no friends. Sweet. Oh and Dan is like, lets go see Sean Paul together! But once again.... hanging out with a 50 yr old when Julia will most definitely be there with Lisa and Deanna and everyone we went with last year is sooo not cool. 
Ew. I hate the fact that she's destroyed my summer so easily. I'm definitely not coming back to ottawa next summer.... I couldn't survive. 

3 more days and then i get a semi-vacation!! sooon.... I'm going to paint my place in ptbo so that should be fun. And I'm going DANCING! and I haven't been since like... april? thats ridiculous for me. so i'm damn excited for that.... now I just have to survive through this torture for a while longer... ugh.

ugh. so i always write so much and then totally forget that ive written somethign and log off. 
i am LAME. 

so im hanging out hurr at cheo once again... working. Apparently over worked. I have the most massive most disgusting cold sore on my face. I feel nasty. 

lol so how young is too young? ive heard half your age +6 is as young as you can go.. but 17 is kinda still a young'un. lol. im only asking because when the older boys come in for their visits im like mmm but then i realize that they're still teenagers and quickly check myself... but i mean, for 18 and 19 yr old boys there are some good looking ones. I can admire them! lol. Misha is in the process of starting a collection for a romantic getaway for him and his girlfriend. Super cute. 

im totally boy crazy i think.... there's a day walker that works here that i actually find attractive LOL. Well whatever... can i be blamed??? Ive been single like a year now, I'm lonely and sex depraved..... I just want some lovin!! hahaha


ahh well, someday my prince will come

Ugh. I dont think its even possible for Julia (aka dirty homeless person) and christina to piss me off even more. They've been training honestly FOREVER, and the dumb bitch STILL doesn't know how to do anything. The two of them together is quite possibly the worst combination of life. Not only do they spend the entire time just chatting and gossiping, Christina's bad habits are rubbing off on her... for example, the incredibly long breaks. And NOTHING gets done, and then I get to play catch up the next time I'm in whatever area she was just trained in. HONESTLY.
